/.idea
/.claude
/.crush
/node_modules/
**/node_modules/**
**/vendor/**
**/dist/**
# Vendored ThirdParty packages ship pre-built dist/ artifacts — keep them.
!**/ThirdParty/**/dist/**
# Admin panel frontend assets must ship with the package so that
# composer-installed apps can serve /__garnet/ without a local build.
!Kernel/Io/GarnetCli/Admin/dist/**
**/WorkDir/**
**/WorkDir/ConfigDev/*
!**/WorkDir/ConfigDev/.keep
# The app template's own WorkDir is shipped scaffolding (dev-default
# app.ini/db.ini/email.ini + .keep placeholders), not a real app's
# runtime state — track it, unlike every WorkDir a scaffolded app grows.
!Templates/Application/WorkDir/**
**/Public/assets/**
**/Public/upload/**
/serve.log
/memory/

.php-cs-fixer.cache
*.js.map
*.css.map
*.gen.css
*.gen.js
*Gen.php
/errors.log
**/errors.log

# Test-scope secret token planted by `php garnet test:provision`.
**/.allow_tests
# Test-mode marker (`php garnet test-mode on`).
**/.test-mode

# Quality tools are composer dev-deps now, never vendored phars.
*.phar

# Node dev-server per-worker logs (tooling/server/garnet-serve.mjs).
/tooling/server/logs/

# AI session checkpoints (local working notes)
/docs/checkpoints/
